ement on the best tools to secure the games.\", \"from\": 9069, \"to\": 9168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the skills\", \"from\": 9085, \"to\": 9095}, {\"ngram\": \"the means\", \"from\": 9100, \"to\": 9109}, {\"ngram\": \"a judgement\", \"from\": 9118, \"to\": 9129}, {\"ngram\": \"the best tools\", \"from\": 9133, \"to\": 9147}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 9158, \"to\": 9167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But we have seen from the French government and from the authorities that the efforts to ensure security in Paris are very professional.\\\"\", \"from\": 9169, \"to\": 9306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9195, \"end\": 9201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999445771788863, \"rank\": 3.300840916942885e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 9277, \"end\": 9282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7546070776395576e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the authorities\", \"from\": 9222, \"to\": 9237}, {\"ngram\": \"the efforts\", \"from\": 9243, \"to\": 9254}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 9265, \"to\": 9273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier in the week, Dubi toldThe Athleticthat the IOC had learned from security issues inParis ahead of the 2022 Champions League final, and insisted on Friday that these security measures were not problematic.\", \"from\": 9308, \"to\": 9519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9359, \"end\": 9362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.089507901616471e-47, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"